        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/e47c2d/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2019-11-03T18:50:11.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I had to google otiose (great word by the way), Around 15 years ago friend of mine turned up with a bottle of the 1966 which was drinking very well and shared a lot of similar characteristics of your note.</p>",
